<div class="row">
	<div class="custom-well span5">
<%= render 'form' %>
	</div>
	<div class="span6">
		<legend>Getting Started</legend>
		<dl>
			<dt>Who can participate?</dt>
			<dd><span color="blue">ShareTheLot</span> is ideal for large residential buildings with assigned parking spots. 
				Don't see your building on the list? Please ask your building's management to 
				<a href="mailto:info@sharethelot.com">contact us</a>.</dd>
		</dl>
		<dl>
			<dt>***6-digit building code***</dt>
			<dd>
				You must have your building code to create an account. If you have lost or 
				forgotten your code please contact your building's management.
				</dd>
		</dl>
		<dl>
			<dt>Share my parking spot:</dt>
			<dd>1. Verify your parking spot(s).</dd>
			<dd>2. Add listings when your parking spot is vacant.</dd>
			<dd>3. Earn <span class="money">money</span> when others use your spot.</dd>
		</dl>
		<dl>
			<dt>Renting a spot:</dt>
			<dd>1. Search for parking.</dd>
			<dd>2. Checkout and print parking passes.</dd>
			<dd>3. Park at your reserved spot and time.</dd>
		</dl>
	</div>
</div>